msgid "essence"
msgid_plural "essence"
msgstr[0] "エッセンス"

msgid ""
"A strange glowing mote of wispy vapor.  It gives off a soothing warmth and "
"feels surprisingly solid, almost alive even."
msgstr ""
"怪しく光る湿り気を帯びた破片です。ほのかに暖かく、非常に硬く、まるで生物のよ"
"うです。"

msgid "blood essence"
msgid_plural "blood essence"
msgstr[0] "エッセンス(血)"

msgid "A strange glowing mote of wispy vapor, drained from a living creature."
msgstr "化け物から排出された、怪しく光る湿り気を帯びた破片です。"

msgid "dull essence"
msgid_plural "dull essence"
msgstr[0] "エッセンス(濁)"

msgid ""
"A dark, powdery bit of strange essence, formed from destructively "
"\"consecrating\" a magic item."
msgstr ""
"粉末状の奇妙な昏いエッセンスです。魔道具を破壊的な方法で「聖化」することで生"
"成されます。"

msgid "crystallized essence"
msgid_plural "crystallized essence"
msgstr[0] "エッセンス(結晶)"

msgid ""
"A tiny sliver of brilliant crystal, formed from otherworldly essence to fuel "
"extremely powerful magic."
msgstr ""
"非常に強力な魔術の源となる、異世界の精髄から作り出した鮮やかな結晶の欠片で"
"す。"

msgid "displacement surge power"
msgid_plural "displacement surge powers"
msgstr[0] "変位サージパワー"

msgid "exotic arrow"
msgid_plural "exotic arrows"
msgstr[0] "矢(異国風)"

msgid ""
"A simple fletched wooden arrow shaft, with an arrowhead carved from some "
"strange material.  Not magical on its own, but can be made into more "
"powerful ammunition.  Stands a very good chance of remaining intact once "
"fired."
msgstr ""
"いくつかの奇妙な材料から彫られた矢じりを備えた、シンプルな木製の矢です。これ"
"自体に効果はありませんが、これを使ってより強力な矢にすることができます。放っ"
"た矢は高確率で再利用できます。"

msgid "exotic bolt"
msgid_plural "exotic bolts"
msgstr[0] "ボルト(異国風)"

msgid ""
"A crossbow bolt radiating strange energy, the head carved from some strange "
"material.  Not magical on its own, but can be made into more powerful "
"ammunition.  Stands a very good chance of remaining intact once fired."
msgstr ""
"いくつかの奇妙な材料から彫られたクロスボウのボルトです。これ自体に効果はあり"
"ませんが、これを使ってより強力なボルトにすることができます。放ったボルトは高"
"確率で再利用できます。"

msgid "searing exotic arrow"
msgid_plural "searing exotic arrows"
msgstr[0] "矢(灼熱/異国風)"

msgid "An arrow radiating strange energy, tipped with a sliver of otherworldly material.  Capable of immolating targets on impact.  Stands a very good chance of remaining intact once fired."
msgstr "奇妙なエネルギーを放射する矢です。異世界の素材の断片が先端に付いています。着弾時に標的を炎上させることができ、非常に高い確率で再利用できます。"

